name: v2.3
body:
## Bug Fixes
- Support uncompressed installation packages #24

## Perf
- browser process judgment
- chrome_plus update status show
- self update slowly

注意：2025/4/25开始，Dev、Canary开始提供未压缩的安装包，路径结构改变导致解压错乱，强烈建议更新到v2.3及以上版本。
Note: Starting from 2025/4/25, Dev and Canary will start to provide uncompressed installation packages. The path structure will cause decompression errors. It is strongly recommended to modify to v2.3 or above.

name: v2.2
body:
## Bug Fixes
-  7z directory error #21
- proxy url compatible protocol
- self update error

## Bug Fixes
- perf: Improve 7z decompression speed #12

注意：由于内置了7z压缩程序，导致程序包体积增大，但是解压速度由原来的几十秒缩减了3-5秒。
Note: Due to the built-in 7z compression program, the package size increases, but the decompression speed is reduced by 3-5 seconds from the original tens of seconds.

name: v1.6
body:
## Bug Fixes
- Fix dev and beta channels on ARM64 By [Bush2021](https://github.com/Bush2021).
- Error displayed when switching language.

## New Features
- Add proxy type, support HTTP(S)、SOCKS5、[GH-PROXY](https://github.com/hunshcn/gh-proxy)，Proxy is only used for chrome++ and updater updates.
- Updater supports online updates.
- Automatically query latest version at startup.
- Update icon.

## Experimental features
Automatically update chrome to the latest version when chrome is not running. This is usually used for canary version updates. It updates once an hour.

实验功能：Chrome每小时定时更新，如果Chrome未运行将完成自动更新，主要用于金丝雀版本的更新，治疗版本强迫症，通常情况下不需要开启，该功能可能存在BUG请谨慎使用
